  "prompt": "What is a suitable solar panel installation provider near Somis, California CA?",
  "response": "As of my last update, there are several solar panel installation providers in and around Somis, California. Here are a few options that could be suitable:\n\n1. **Revolution Solar**\n   - Revolution Solar specializes in custom solar panel installations for residential and commercial properties. They offer services such as system design, installation, and maintenance.\n\n2. **Solar Power Systems**\n   - Located nearby in Ventura, Solar Power Systems provides comprehensive solar solutions including installation, maintenance, and financial consultation to help maximize savings on energy bills.\n\n3. **Sunrun**\n   - Sunrun is a nationally recognized solar company that has local branches throughout California. They offer solar panel leasing and purchasing options, along with home batteries and backup solutions.\n\n4. **SolarWorld**\n   - SolarWorld is another highly reputable company that offers tailored solar solutions, including residential solar systems, financing options, and ongoing support.\n\n5. **California Solar Electric**\n   - Based in Ojai, California Solar Electric has over 20 years of experience in providing solar energy solutions. They are known for their excellent customer service and high-quality installations.\n\nBefore selecting a provider, it is recommended to check recent reviews and ratings, seek multiple quotes, and compare the specific services and warranties offered by each company to find the best fit for your needs.\n\nIf you conduct a local search or look at recent reviews, you might find updated information and new providers as well.",
